WEBVTT

00:01.720 --> 00:05.061
How would you like to try out for the Santos Football Club?

00:06.333 --> 00:09.309
He's only 15, he's never even left Bauru.

00:16.587 --> 00:19.415
Ginga style might have worked for you back in Santos...

00:19.605 --> 00:22.077
...but it will never hold up at an international level.

00:24.543 --> 00:25.949
I can't play like the other guys.

00:26.568 --> 00:29.567
What's wrong with not playing the way the other guys do?

00:30.210 --> 00:31.463
Show us what happens...

00:32.652 --> 00:37.030
...when you have the courage to embrace who you truly are.

00:48.300 --> 00:52.004
You may be 16 years old but you're now a spokesman for this great nation.

